y meal, and Virginia once chose sushi for her celebration. Here’s a look at what it looked like.\n    &lt;\\p&gt;\n  </p>\n</section>\n<title>\n  Orchid Garden Restaurant\n</title>\n<section>\n  <p>\n    As mentioned above, Paul and Virginia on the restaurant for a while on Orcas Island. It was called the Orchid Garden. It's served pan-asian cuisine. </p>\n</section>\n<title>\n  Orchid Garden Restaurant\n</title>\n<section>\n  <p>\n    This is the inside of the Orchid Garden restaurant. Paul and Virginia spent a lot of time, energy and money and remodeling the restaurant. \n  </p>\n</section>\n<title>\n  Orchid Garden Restaurant\n</title>\n<section>\n  <p>\n    This is the bar inside the Orchid Garden restaurant. \n  </p>\n</section>\n<title>\n  Orchid Garden Restaurant\n</title>\n<section>\n  <p>\n    This is one of the dishes from the Orchid Garden \n  </p>\n</section>	2024-11-16 08:43:01.457896	2024-11-29 18:39:53.425663	
